_______________________________________________________________________________
"Ultrablast"       
        This is the ultimate psionic attack.  It hurls a blast of mental
        energy every couple seconds for a length of time dependent on
        guild level.  The power of each individual blast is also dependent
        on guild level.  This power is taxing on the mind.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  15	Potential Points:  7
 
Command:  ultrablast <target>
